An '''FX-9 surgical assistant''',<ref name="ECUC">''[[Star Wars Character Encyclopedia: Updated and Expanded]]''</ref> also known as the '''FX-9 ''', was a [[FX-series medical assistant droid|FX-series]] [[medical droid]] manufactured by [[Medtech Industries]]. During [[Anakin Skywalker|Darth Vader's]] reconstruction after his [[Duel on Mustafar|duel]] with [[Obi-Wan Kenobi]], a FX-9 supplied the wounded [[Sith Lord]] with a blood transfusion.<ref name="Ultimate" />

{{Droid-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The FX-9 surgical assistant was identified as the [[FX-6/Legends|FX-6]] medical droid in "Every Droid in Star Wars", a video posted on [[StarWarsKids.com]] in [[2019]].<ref name="Kids">{{SWKidsYouTube|series=Star Wars By the Numbers|text=Every Droid in Star Wars|video=UQg6aX7lqTA|nolive=1}}</ref>

